TITLE: Episode 93 - The Vixens Talkin' Over Adam Patrick
DESCRIPTION: Hosted by Adam Patrick, the Vixens join in on the fun of his show Yer Talkin Over me. He gets them to discuss their own personal evolutions, thoughts on morality, natural order, and some of what they think the key building blocks of Ancapistan would be.
